Project 1
ReadMe

Compilation
•	To compile simple use the make all command. This will compile both the client and server.

Running the Client
•	To run the client run this command: ./client [option] [URL] [port]

Running the Server
•	To run the server run this command: ./server [port]
•	Can be terminated with SIGTERM

Connecting to the Server with the Client
•	In order to connect to this server: ./server 7890, run this client: ./client ccc.wpi.edu/index.html 7890
•	For the HTML file either index.html or TMDG.html can be specified
